\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">幫手既可以入tg群t.me/standbyhk2019</a><br />\n<br />\n類如遲下想要有咩產品上架咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/standbyhk2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstandbyhk2019&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=656494ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/standbyhk2019</a> <br />\n<br />\n同埋真係好需要大家支持同幫助嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵貨源/搞運輸 整間公司出黎其實唔係咁易嫁葉師傅<br />\n<br />\n試過入中路但變左洪金寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家幫幫拖出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6abdac8d5774ae235dd236f49e59f7073281b1b","tid":1672681,"uid":187007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a082e21017de026c8452eabdbab1f5f3bea1280","tid":1672681,"uid":86204,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"本身已經有啦 做咩姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"本身有咩？"},{"pid":"e167f7811696923393fada35c244b902a8e6ab3c","tid":1672681,"uid":14366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"Google &ldquo;光時&rdquo;"},{"pid":"c878058b916e99fabf3e634c37a2fee1c8c347e9","tid":1672681,"uid":186811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6abdac8d5774ae235dd236f49e59f7073281b1b","tid":1672681,"uid":187007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a082e21017de026c8452eabdbab1f5f3bea1280","tid":1672681,"uid":86204,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"本身已經有啦 做咩姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"本身有咩？"},"cit